{"title":"死不了草","authors":["孟瑞凌"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":5,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"死不了草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孟瑞凌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从遥远的山坳，寄给我——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗少女纯朴、羞涩的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村般清秀、美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如那向往自由的蒲公英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说，它——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"株永远不会枯死的小草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要伏贴着大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有顽强的生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管不是安泰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不畏惧飓风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我收下了，饱含着感激的热泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收下了你的深情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这株永不会枯的“死不了”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻进记忆，珍藏进心灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类、友谊与蓝天同在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向阳光和你交出真诚的心。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}